<plot>The leopard and his friend the Ethiopian hunt for animals (like the kudu) on the veldt. The animals move to the jungle, into the shade, for safety. The leopard himself visits the jungle, and discovers that his prey are well hidden in the mixture of sun and shadows that exists beneath the canopy. The leopard must adapt also, in order to survive.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?452830</url></doc>
